Package Entities

Class Project

java.lang.Object
Entities.Project
public class Project extends Object
Represents a Project in the FYP Management System. Each project can be classified with 1 of the 4 status: RESERVED, ALLOCATED, AVAILABLE, UNAVILABLE
Since:
2023-04-14
Version:
1.0
Author:
